      <accessrestrict id="aspace_26e548d9a18728a9da0504f991144a55">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>
         <p>Box 8, postcards, must be used under the supervision of a Public Services staff member at the front table.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_2ca08e1481d77d2894c6ec80865afda8">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The German Poster and Postcard Collection consists of approximately 2400 posters and 150 postcards from East and West Germany depicting countercultural, political, and propaganda themes from the 1970s to 1990. A small number of newspapers and pamphlets are included in the collection.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
